Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到花該是件多高興的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的不是送花的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 誰送花會比較高興？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦 是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉紅害羞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯的那個初夏的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也照舊到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水星大潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去參加鳳尾舟協會的會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚應該就能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天暖洋洋的呢 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是亞利亞公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在長靴小路等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超快的速度給我趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用超快的速度哦 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}總覺得有點害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}哎呀 妳丈夫送給妳的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}今天一天都很緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不知道我能不能收到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:26.29,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 伯克洛節上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸前戴著紅玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子 妳太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生 拉頭髮禁止啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不是鬢子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？誰叫妳的鬢角這麼多破綻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝了整整一筐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是想啊…送給艾莉西亞小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 絕佳的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天可是男人給愛慕之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送上一朵玫瑰的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那已經不止一朵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺對艾莉西亞小姐的崇高的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一朵花來表達怎麼夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有把全城的玫瑰都買下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能表達我無限的愛意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生一個人拿不了這麼多花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才叫我來幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該覺得光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的女孩們也都戴著花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲也收到玫瑰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是麵包屋的叔叔送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是友情玫瑰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 難道這也是友情玫瑰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 妳說那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是曉先生要送給艾莉西亞前輩的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為那是燈里前輩從不同的人那裡收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雅典娜前輩一大早就收到了一堆玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司的後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 她好像有很多小孩子的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲也送給雅典娜前輩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不送友情玫瑰主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算我送玫瑰給她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只不過是多了一朵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對雅典娜前輩來說 沒有什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得雅典娜前輩會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給她的話 她會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼涼的石板路好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水面上倒映著天空 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾曬的衣物 建築物的格子窗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有浮島呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像在鏡子之國裡一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊 讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哥斯拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我哥斯拉 你這個馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我馬尾男 妳這只哥斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯拉哥斯拉哥斯拉哥斯拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男馬尾男…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華也收到玫瑰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是阿魯送的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是阿魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 是我要送給艾莉西亞前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說馬尾男…那些玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要送給艾莉西亞前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有一朵花是無法展現我的心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 燈里 艾莉西亞前輩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去參加鳳尾舟協會的會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬尾男 我會搶先把花送給艾莉西亞前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭哥斯拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 本大爺就要用數量壓倒一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿曉～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 燈里 妳好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多玫瑰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這些幾乎都是送給晃前輩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋的晃小姐似乎很受女孩子歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年我都要給她投遞很多玫瑰的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是晃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是阿曉你托我買的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒給我錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 先欠著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你要拒絕老朋友的請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是阿曉 你上次借的和上上次借的都還…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候我把脆脆冰中獎的雪糕棒給了你對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴我你不記得這個恩情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這麼久以前的事情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要中獎的雪糕棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭得滿地打滾的那個是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想我把那件事添油加醋地告訴鬢子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里小姐 我還要幹活 先走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請加油工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要表達本大爺的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點玫瑰遠遠不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你就不能再便宜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜不了就是便宜不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀你就再便宜一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}我可是全都買光哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯克洛到底是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯克洛是花蕾的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給妳講講伯克洛節的由來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伯克洛節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性無論老少都會給愛慕的人送上一朵紅玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個節日的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傳統的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是數百年前發生在地球上的真實故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個愛上了高貴姑娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下級貴族青年的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個青年為了向姑娘的父親展示自己的誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自告奮勇地上了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不幸的青年在戰鬥中受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終體力不支而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他倒下的地方恰好是一片白玫瑰花叢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年拚盡最後一絲氣力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘下一朵玫瑰交給了戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘收到被青年的鮮血染紅的白玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知了自己的愛人已經戰死的噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個悲傷的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也很浪漫不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玫瑰象徵著永恆的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有這樣一個故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你砍完價了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 本大爺完勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的很不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事的男女主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經在數百年前過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但青年的愛仍舊化作紅色玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直流傳到了今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鳳尾舟協會的會議剛剛結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢了一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 在亞利亞公司門前等會比較快吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老家在浮島上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在那裡待到昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正準備回地下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星大潮的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐的公司都放假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是開店歇業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天還是伯克洛節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那朵玫瑰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是我自己買來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想送給艾莉西亞前輩的玫瑰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…我說這是別人送的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯會是什麼樣的表情呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐對寶石有興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶石？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎麼突然想起問這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「玫瑰之瞳」的寶石原石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下世界偶爾能挖到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰之瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過竟然借玫瑰的話題送我寶石原石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…莫非這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藍華 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好啊 燈里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 曉君也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 阿魯 好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 妳見到艾莉西亞前輩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這是怎麼回事啊 曉君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多玫瑰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是本大爺為了表達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}比大海還要深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}比浮島還要高遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}對艾莉西亞小姐的愛意才買下的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯送我這塊石頭的含義…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是熱情的氣候調節員 曉君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 晃前輩好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我見到伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他投遞了好多送給晃前輩的玫瑰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…每年都是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐 妳發燒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我沒什麼問題啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？剛才？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 還是先幫我找艾莉西亞前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍…藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣就做好萬全的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是送玫瑰的練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子啊 拜託妳演一下艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的…心…心…心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習就這麼緊張怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的表情好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 而且妳演的艾莉西亞小姐一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還挺有自信的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演得不像還這麼緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那見到真人會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣我也無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拜託妳陪我練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們再來一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 艾莉西亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟協會的會議結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我正準備回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多玫瑰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是工作關係上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從熟客和聯絡處那裡收到了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的心…心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 燈里才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從曉君那裡收到了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打擾你們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…艾 艾莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亞利亞社長！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞小姐！Come back！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back…back…back…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音 傳不到那邊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個廢柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋪滿了整個水面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直 延伸到遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像 很久以前那對戀人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照在人心中蔓延開來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人對另外一個人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那溫柔又略帶哀愁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給每個人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都帶來了和煦的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不可思議地換上笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色玫瑰的傳說所施下的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐 關於剛才那個玫瑰之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍加雕琢就會變得很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的寶石一定很適合藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也有紅色玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}日語中五花肉與玫瑰有部分發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子的冷笑話 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是地球上流傳已久的文字遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找到艾莉西亞前輩之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要陪著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能傳達給艾莉西亞前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那毫無根據的自信是從哪來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳陪了我一天的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次收到男孩子送的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一朵紅玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說無論是男性還是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到花都會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送上一朵紅玫瑰的伯克洛節
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在水星大潮的城市中的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鮮豔的玫瑰紅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯得是那麼的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是個小小的紀念日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐 能度過美好的一天真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色玫瑰的傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個悲傷的愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有點讓人憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些 樸實的星光…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:02:02.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:15.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:30.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:43.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:50.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:57.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:05.09,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:15.40,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:02:02.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:15.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:30.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:43.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:50.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:57.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了豔麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:05.09,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:15.40,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:57.04,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨が上がる 遠く空眺め 雲の切れ間探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:08.89,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもよりも 少し遠回り 海へ続く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:16.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}切りすぎた前髪 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:21.23,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そのまま 駆け出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:28.11,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をかすめていく 風の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:33.71,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか夏のはじまりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:39.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}大きく手を振って 深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:45.53,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}この時間を抱きしめていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:50.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}明日もまた会えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:57.04,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨過天晴 眺望遙遠的天空 探尋雲彩的縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:08.89,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}繞過早已習慣的歸途 向著通往大海的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:16.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}忘掉剪得過短的留海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:21.23,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}毫無顧忌地大膽前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:28.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}吹拂著面頰的海風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:33.71,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不知何時染上了初夏的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:39.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}用力揮揮手 來個深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:45.53,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}滿心希望永遠擁抱這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:50.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}明天 我們還會再見嗎


